Item: Artur Hefczyc: 2.5.0 version of Tigase server available
<http://www.tigase.org/node/218>
Date: 2007-02-03 16:56:24 UTC
This time changes are very small but also very significant.

Following suggestions from Jabber/XMPP community I changed the policy for packets forwarding. Previously all unknown XMPP stanzas were rejected by default. After a few discussions I realized that this is not the way Jabber/XMPP server is supposed to work.

As a result PacketFilter class has been created which takes care of all unknown XMPP stanzas. By default it just forwards all stanzas to destination address if the destination address is not the local server.

